name: Hashmasks
description:

Are you a curious lover of fine art? Join our community of passionate detectives. Come add to the Hashmasks story and discover the character behind your own mask!

name: ENS: Ethereum Name Service
description: Ethereum Name Service (ENS) domains are secure domain names for the decentralized world. ENS domains provide a way for users to map human readable names to blockchain and non-blockchain resources, like Ethereum addresses, IPFS hashes, or website URLs. ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.

description: Fox Fam is a collection of generative characters, designed by Yum Yum Studio. The foxes are created from a set of lovingly handcrafted attributes giving each one their own unique character. We have released 10,000 foxes into the wild for you to own!

name: Cool Pets NFT
description: An NFT offering from the Cool Cats brand, Pets is a collection of 19,999 NFTs that are procedurally generated based on item interaction. All Pets start as an Egg and evolve into their final form, which represents one of four elements: Grass, Fire, Water, or Air. Users can evolve their Pet through our gamified experience on [coolcatsnft.com](https://coolcatsnft.com)â€“your final Pet is one of 17 million possible outcomes! To learn more about Pets, Eggs, and the world of Cooltopia, visit [cooltopia.coolcatsnft.com](https://cooltopia.coolcatsnft.com). We love the Pets!

name: Galaxy-Eggs
description:
Galaxy Warriors Official Link - https://opensea.io/collection/galaxy-warriors-9999

(art)ificial is an art studio that explores the boundaries of technology and art. Our first project is Galaxy Eggs - a generative collection of 9,999 Eggs of the metaverse that live on the Ethereum Blockchain. name: Omnimorphs
description:
Omnimorphs are mimetic mysterious entities on Earth able to merge and evolve through [OmniFusion](https://fusion.omnimorphs.com). The Fusion utility gives owners the opportunity to combine two of their tokens customising the look & rarity of their avatar. The NFT collection was originally made of 10,000 hand-crafted artworks created by digital artist,  [DÃ¡niel Taylor](https://twitter.com/DanielTaylorArt). This number decreases as every Fusion burns an Omnimorph, gifting its owner with a [Soul Shard](https://opensea.io/collection/omni-fusion) in return. 

**Our vision is to create a supportive and curious NFT art collective where real value overcomes hype and excellence subdues glitz.**

Read about [our Vision](https://omnimorphs.medium.com/omnimorphs-our-vision-for-2022-f210d0e0886b).

Lore, webshop, and more on our [website](https://omnimorphs.com).
